Description
-----------

Enables/disables [antialiasing](Antialiasing "Antialiasing") and sets by how much the scenes are antialiased.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_multisamples [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - Number of samples to use by anti-aliasing. (2, 4, 8, 16)

